timelineItems.text: Come on you burgundy boys! #COLvVAN http://t.co/U2lJpg7koD

timelineItems.name: Jesse Trujillo
timelineItems.text: #Rapids96 Coach Pablo Mastroeni going with the 3-3-4 formation Torres, Solignac & Ramirez all up top.

timelineItems.name: Asif Hossain
timelineItems.text: I don't understand what I just watched. Disgusting. Worst piece of refereeing to date this year, that's saying something. #MLS #VWFC

timelineItems.name: John Molinaro
timelineItems.text: Sorry, but why did the refs call back that Whitecaps goal? Where, exactly, was the foul? #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Erik Hedin
timelineItems.text: What?!? That beauty wasn't a goal?!? Ridiculous. #VWFC

timelineItems.desc: Kevin Doyle (Colorado Rapids) is shown the yellow card.
timelineItems.title: YELLOW CARD: Kevin Dole is booked for an off-the-ball foul.

timelineItems.name: Vancouver Whitecaps
timelineItems.text: Over. Rivero drives one over the bar after a threatening run. #VWFC #COLvVAN

timelineItems.name: Simon Fudge
timelineItems.text: In training and in games, Rivero strikes the ball over the bar far too much... #COLvVAN #MLS

timelineItems.name: Major League Soccer
timelineItems.text: That flick from Torres, though 👌 #COLvVAN https://t.co/k4jwWsfe5a

timelineItems.name: Daniel Boniface
timelineItems.text: We're into the 90th minute. #Rapids96 with a 1-0 lead. 11-game home winless streak in danger. #COLvVAN

timelineItems.name: Colorado Rapids
timelineItems.text: CHANCE: Sanchez and @LuchoSoli break but the latter squares the ball when he might have shot (90) 1-0 #COLvVAN

timelineItems.name: Daniel Boniface
timelineItems.text: Very nice counter attack by Solignac and Sanchez... Solignac cuts back to Sanchez in front of goal but can't find him. #Rapids96 #COLvVan

timelineItems.desc: Attempt missed. Kendall Waston (Vancouver Whitecaps FC) header from the centre of the box is high and wide to the left. Assisted by Jordan Harvey
timelineItems.title: MISS: Kendall Waston's stoppage time effort goes over the bar

timelineItems.name: Colorado Rapids
timelineItems.text: COME. ON. #RAPIDS96. (90) 1-0 #COLvVAN

timelineItems.name: Asif Hossain
timelineItems.text: I assume because most of these referees are just actors hired to play referees on TV. #MLS #VWFC https://t.co/07UU3AMidr

timelineItems.name: Vancouver Whitecaps
timelineItems.text: Over the bar. Waston, who's no an auxiliary striker. Nods it over. #VWFC #COLvVAN

timelineItems.name: Jayson Kirby
timelineItems.text: #VWFC put on a pretty lacklustre display of football tonight… Just terrible. Made the Rapids look good tonight.

timelineItems.name: Denver Post Rapids
timelineItems.text: FINAL: #Rapids96 defeat Vancouver Whitecaps 1-0, ending their 11-game winless streak at home http://t.co/QpjdPx2kDH

timelineItems.name: Stout St. Bulldogs
timelineItems.text: They’ve done it! Rapids win at home over Vancouver! 1-0! #rapids96

timelineItems.name: @CapTied96
timelineItems.text: I feel like I have seen the Golden Palace of the Himalayas with my own two eyes. The #Rapids96 actually won a match at home and I was there.

timelineItems.name: Inside MLS
timelineItems.text: FULL TIME: Colorado Rapids 1 - Vancouver Whitecaps 0 #COLvVAN #MLS

timelineItems.name: Jonathan
timelineItems.text: O'DOYLE RULES #COLvVAN
